{"tid":2463193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜：堅定支持被制裁9名公民揭露新疆侵犯人權","createTime":"2021-03-26T13:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:41:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1750bc64aa4dfffbe846f6e87ed37bad6f73274","tid":2463193,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582816-20210326.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582816-20210326.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=012bd365\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582816-20210326.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b9ada438\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582816-20210326.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中方宣布對英方9名人員和4個實體實施制裁。英國首相約翰遜表示，堅定地支持被中方制裁的9名英國公民，約翰遜表示，他們在揭露新疆維吾爾穆斯林人權遭嚴重侵犯的事件中，扮演重要角色，行使言論自由等基本權利。<br />\n<br />\n外相藍韜文亦表示，與被制裁的人士站在同一陣線，強調絕不會阻止他們就新疆出現侵犯人權的事宜發聲，藍韜文表示，若果北京否認有關事宜，就應該允許聯合國人權事務專員到當地。英國外交部將召見中國駐英大使，討論中國對英國實施的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，美國與幾個西方盟友，將黑手伸向新疆雪白的棉花，污衊新疆存在強迫勞動，甚至種族滅絕。華春瑩重申中國光明磊落，事實將刺破所有針對中國的謠言。"},{"pid":"62f71d7dcceca66d821e10edc934f194bdc26b90","tid":2463193,"uid":201751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍韜文"},{"pid":"8dc3148ef5c91b3ead20f79567ad7482ce22fc8c","tid":2463193,"uid":73276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1750bc64aa4dfffbe846f6e87ed37bad6f73274","tid":2463193,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582816-20210326.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582816-20210326.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=012bd365\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582816-20210326.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b9ada438\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582816-20210326.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中方宣布對英方9名人員和4個實體實施制裁。英國首相約翰遜表示，堅定地支持被中方制裁的9名英國公民，約翰遜表示，他們在揭露新疆維吾爾穆斯林人權遭嚴重侵犯的事件中，扮演重要角色，行使言論自由等基本權利。<br />\n<br />\n外相藍韜文亦表示，與被制裁的人士站在同一陣線，強調絕不會阻止他們就新疆出現侵犯人權的事宜發聲，藍韜文表示，若果北京否認有關事宜，就應該允許聯合國人權事務專員到當地。英國外交部將召見中國駐英大使，討論中國對英國實施的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，美國與幾個西方盟友，將黑手伸向新疆雪白的棉花，污衊新疆存在強迫勞動，甚至種族滅絕。華春瑩重申中國光明磊落，事實將刺破所有針對中國的謠言。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:39:24.000Z","msg":"明明政府保護人民只係份內事<br />\n但我居然因為咁就覺得英國好好<br />\n<br />\n唉，來生不做香港人"},{"pid":"18f411d0ade4dfc75184e873a9faf74a7e7d966f","tid":2463193,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35114e3de92ecc762bf79ff36bc8ed87a0c7be39","tid":2463193,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcEytEuvkVC6wRFHrtL9bxdmLmKqUyoyrqgd9zTgCLLro?filename=scUvduE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscUvduE.gif&h=a8514e2b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}